com.fico.streamvar.api.profile

Class MergeableProfileRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fico.streamvar.api.profile.MergeableProfileRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public abstract class MergeableProfileRecord
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A mergeable global profile record class must extend from this class in order to enable merging. In addition to that, the MergeableModelStep interface must be implemented by the model step that is to perform the merging.
